### ChatClient API Test Requests
### You can use these with IntelliJ IDEA HTTP Client or similar tools

### 1. Simple Chat
POST http://localhost:8080/api/chat/simple
Content-Type: text/plain

Tell me a short joke about Spring Framework

### 2. Chat with System Prompt
POST http://localhost:8080/api/chat/system
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What is Spring AI?",
  "systemPrompt": "You are an expert in Spring Framework and AI technologies. Provide concise but informative answers."
}

### 3. Templated Chat
POST http://localhost:8080/api/chat/template
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "template": "Write a haiku about {topic} in {language}",
  "params": {
    "topic": "Spring Boot",
    "language": "English"
  }
}

### 4. Chat with Metadata
POST http://localhost:8080/api/chat/metadata
Content-Type: text/plain

Explain the benefits of using Spring AI for enterprise applications

### 5. Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/chat/health
